content: Lakeshore Surgical Center's quality assurance committee reviewed case VS-8294 involving Konnor Zielinski (DOB 06/04/1987). The 9-hour procedure on 09/12/2023 utilized experimental biocompatible stabilizers (study ID: SPI-09X). Post-operative complications included CSF leakage, managed with blood patching. Patient discharged to Horizonview Rehab on 09/22 under supervising physician Dr. A. Mirani (ext. 73230).
